body_html:
Isn't that equivalent to passing enqueue_many=True to tf.train.batch?

On Oct 11, 2016 1:50 PM, "Yandi Xia" notifications@github.com wrote:

@ebrevdo https://github.com/ebrevdo
I don't specify batch size in the placeholder.
I enqueue a batch of instances into the queue (variable size of batches)
each time.
And each dequeue will return a batch of data.

Thanks.
